keyMappings:
mapkey j h
mapkey k j
mapkey l k
mapkey ; l
mapkey t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection

map gf LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map gt duplicateTab
map gp togglePinTab
map gm toggleMuteTab
map : goForward
map J goBack

unmap L
unmap K
unmap yt
unmap gT
unmap ^
unmap g0
unmap g$
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap zH
unmap zL
unmap gf
unmap gF
unmap T
unmap <a-f>
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
